text: Waleed Al-Mohamed Abdulmuhsin (born 10 July 1961) is a Kuwaiti rower. He competed in the men's single sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Kuwaiti male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Kuwait Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
